properties.Name: CustomerAssetOwnership
properties.Description: An asset that is owned by a customer over the indicated period.

Columns.Name: CustomerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer.

Columns.Name: CustomerAssetId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer Asset.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date that the customer had an ownership position in the customer asset.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date that the customer had an ownership position in the customer asset.

Columns.Name: CustomerAssetOwnershipNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding a customer asset ownership.

Columns.Name: CustomerAssetOwnershipPercent
Columns.Description: The percentage of the customer asset that the customer has ownership of.

Columns.Name: CustomerAssetOwnershipValue
Columns.Description: The value (amount) of the customer asset hat the customer has ownership of.
